Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.54,0:18:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 是面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看得到
